Terminals unused in grammar

    RETURN


Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: INT MAIN NL BEG NL decl NL assign NL loop NL END

    2 decl: INT ID '[' NUMBER ']' SC

    3 assign: INT ID EQ ID '[' NUMBER ']' SC

    4 loop: FOR ID EQ NUMBER TO ID '-' NUMBER DO NL IF ID '[' ID ']' RELOP ID NL ID EQ ID '[' ID ']' SC NL ENDIF NL ENDFOR


